      <article class="dest-card reveal" id="materuni-waterfall-and-coffee-farm-tour">
        <div class="dest-visual"><img src="/images/daytrip-materuni.jpg" alt="Materuni Falls near Moshi, on the lower slopes of Mount Kilimanjaro" width="800" height="500" loading="lazy"><span class="trip-price">From $91 Per person</span></div>
