        <div class="dest-body">
          <div class="dest-tags"><span class="dest-tag">Kilimanjaro</span><span class="dest-tag">Day Trip</span></div>
          <h3 class="dest-name">Kilimanjaro Helicopter Tour</h3>
          <p class="dest-desc">Experience the ultimate luxury adventure and skip the grueling multi-day trek to see the rooftop of Africa. This exclusive scenic flight lifts you high above the clouds, providing a thrilling, birds-eye perspective of Mount Kilimanjaro&#39;s majestic snow-capped peaks, dramatic volcanic craters, and ancient glacial walls.</p>
          <details class="trip-details">
            <summary>See itinerary &amp; details</summary>
            <h4>Highlights</h4>
            <ul><li>Soar directly past the iconic, snow-dusted Uhuru Peak and the jagged crags of Mawenzi.</li><li>Enjoy unmatched aerial photography opportunities of East Africa&#39;s most famous geographic landmark.</li><li>Experience a premium, comfortable journey with a professional pilot providing live commentary.</li></ul>
            <h4>Itinerary</h4>
            <ol><li>06:30 AM: Morning pick-up from your hotel and transfer to the Arusha Airport or assigned helipad.</li><li>07:15 AM: Meet your pilot, review safety protocols, and map out the flight path.</li><li>07:30 AM: Lift off and fly towards the mountain as the morning light hits the plains.</li><li>08:00 AM: Spend unforgettable minutes soaring around the Kibo caldera, ice fields, and dramatic alpine desert zones.</li><li>08:45 AM: Fly back over the lush montane forest belt and touch down safely.</li><li>09:30 AM: Transfer back to your hotel in time for a late breakfast.</li></ol>
            <h4>What is Included</h4><p>VIP private helicopter flight, fuel, professional pilot, airport/landing fees, hotel transfers, and a celebratory glass of champagne or juice upon landing.</p>
